ral","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"appropriations to the Fund for activities of the Fund; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"reimbursement from Federal agencies for the activities described in paragraphs (1), (2), and (4) of subsection (a), which shall only be from amounts made available in advance in appropriations Acts for such reimbursement.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Expenditures","label":"2 Expenditures","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any expenditure from the Fund for the purposes of this part shall be made from amounts available in the Fund from a deposit described in paragraph (1), and amounts available in the Fund shall be in addition to any other appropriations available to the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency for such purposes.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Supplement not supplant","label":"c Supplement not supplant","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Amounts in the Fund shall be used to supplement, not supplant, other Federal, State, local, or Tribal funding for activities in response to a declaration.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Reporting","label":"d Reporting","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t6/s677c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft6%2Fs677c%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall require an entity that receives amounts from the Fund to submit a report to the Secretary that details the specific use of the amounts.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
